high_descs: Turn left, walk to the wall, and then turn right to the tv cabinet.
Pick up the  newsletter to the left of the tv.
Take a few steps backwards from where you are.
Pull out the third bottom drawer from your left side and place the newsletter in it.
Turn around and head towards the sofa.
Pick up the newsletter on the sofa.
Turn around and head towards the third bottom drawer from your left side.
Place the newsletter in the drawer and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place the two newsletters in a tv drawer.

high_descs: Go to the left side of the desk that is in front of you.
Pick up the newspaper from the desk.
Back away from the desk a little bit and look down at the drawers.
Put the newspaper in the third bottom drawer from the left.
Turn the opposite direction and go to the right side of the loveseat.
Pick up the newspaper from the loveseat.
Turn around and return to the desk.
Put the newspaper in the third bottom drawer from the left, on top of the first newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers away in a drawer.

high_descs: move to the dresser in front of the couch
pick up a paper from the dresser
move to the front of the dresser in front of the couch
put the paper in a drawer in the dresser
move to couch behind you
pick up the paper from the couch
move to the front of the dresser in front of the couch
put the paper in a drawer in the dresser
anns.task_desc: Put two papers in a drawer.
